Program: Discovery
Title: The Infinite Monkey Cage USA Tour: Chicago
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p034cf9b
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 13 Oct 2015
Brian Cox and Robin Ince take to the stage in Chicago, Illinois, to discuss fossil records and evolution. They are joined on stage by host of NPR's "Wait Wait Don't Tell Me" Peter Sagal, comedian and Saturday Night Live alumnus Julia Sweeney, palaeontologist Paul Sereno and evolutionary biologist Jerry Coyne. (Photo: Robin Ince (left) and Brian Cox) Show less